        android:layout_height="match_parent"
        android:layout_marginTop="8dp"
        android:padding="5dp"
        android:text="Q9.  Whether do you prescribe books for studying the syllabus ?"
        android:textColor="@android:color/background_dark"
        android:textSize="20sp" />

        <TextView
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="match_parent"
            android:layout_marginTop="8dp"
            android:padding="5dp"
            android:text="A. In every section of the subject, experts recommend a particular book for studying. Students need to follow the SAVE classes, where the book has been prescribed clearly. It has been observed that SAVE classes along with PDF text (which are a post-"
